pan style=\"color: #000000;\">个社区，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">2018</span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">年底前，实现全市城乡“互联网</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">+</span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">社区之家”建设全覆盖。</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '“互联网+社区之家”迎来全国创建文明城市工作经验交流会代表一行莅临参观', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '460-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-10 13:05:48', '2017-04-10 05:05:48', '', 460, 'http://www.jsssha.com/?p=467', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
